SELECT
    'MATERIAL_SPEC' AS cabn_filter,
    in0.OBJEK,
    in0.ATWRT,
    in1.OBJEK MAT_NUM
FROM
    in0
        INNER JOIN
    in1 ON in0.OBJEK = in1.CUOBJ
        INNER JOIN
    in2 ON in0.ATINN = in2.ATINN AND in2.ATNAM = 'MATERIAL_SPEC'
UNION
SELECT
    'SPEC_REV_LEVEL',
    in0.OBJEK,
    in0.ATWRT,
    in1.OBJEK MAT_NUM
FROM
    in0
        INNER JOIN
    in1 ON in0.OBJEK = in1.CUOBJ
        INNER JOIN
    in2 ON in0.ATINN = in2.ATINN AND in2.ATNAM = 'SPEC_REV_LEVEL'
